{"tid":1924904,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"想救連登？我有一個辦法","createTime":"2020-03-14T03:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T04:12:49.000Z","uid":263944,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a72a786954a2a1b8cdb36b2acc3f14d9557a2454","tid":1924904,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T03:50:01.000Z","msg":"相信唔只我一個見到連登因為肺炎同五毛搞到烏煙瘴氣。六月既連登同依家既連登最大分別係邊呢？<br />\n<br />\n答案係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聚焦</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n當時我地有<span style=\"color: red;\">清晰而且統一既討論</span>，所以有能力令100萬，200萬人出黎。<br />\n<br />\n到抗爭成熟既依家，我哋有勇武戰線，twitter戰線，黃藍經濟戰線，tvb戰線，連儂戰線.....我哋嘅資源因為<span style=\"color: red;\">戰線過多而分散</span>晒，一方便導致力量變細，另一方面導致五毛有機可乘。<br />\n<br />\n總上所說，要光復連登，就要<span style=\"color: red;\">聚焦行動</span>，咁先可以令行動走出連登，reach到200萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我建議先聚焦文宣戰線，進行集中的外國文宣、改革連儂牆機制（人手一post-it），推行每周家課表，靈活地適應肺炎，在家抗爭。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n期望見到既效果係熱門po全部都係關於twitter、reddit嘅 新手po、組隊連結、罐頭文宣、文宣圖、做文宣嘅文宣。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復<span style=\"color: orange;\">連登</span>，時代革命！</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要改革自己，適應新既環境。香港人，Be Water！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1N7yecp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1N7yecp.gif&h=56705d71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"454acefda5d2855c3e3d4bd5d1417ce3023749d4","tid":1924904,"uid":219583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"直接搞個抗爭討論區唔好?<br />\n係要光復連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登本身就係膠POST多 我唔明點解你地班友要霸住個連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7b1cfa0d71ea8bf5445e80da530027c1524deb","tid":1924904,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a72a786954a2a1